### 1. Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "security.test@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123",
  "firstName": "Security",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "security.test@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123"
}

> {%
 client.global.set("authToken", response.body.token);
 client.global.set("currentUserId", response.body.id);
 %}

### 3. Access Protected Profile (Authorized)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/profile/{{currentUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 4. Access Protected Profile (Unauthorized - No Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/profile/{{currentUserId}}

### 5. Access Admin Endpoint (Should be Forbidden for CLIENT role)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/applications/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
